'''WTAI'''

Wireless Telephone Applications Interface - The wireless telephone applications interface (WTAI) can be used in conjunction with the Wireless Application Protocol ([[WAP]]).  WAP is an open international standard for applications that use wireless communication.  The Wireless Telephone Application Interface allows a phone number to be linked to a web page.  

For example

<a href="wtai://wp/mc;1234 1234">1234 1234</a>

